          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Yiddish</add>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>, <date>Sunday,
                                                  29th Sivan (<del>May</del> June), 1851</date></p>
                              <p>To my friend the wise, etc., etc:</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">That which I sent you, you can advertise in the
                                                  <date>August</date><lb/> number. On the
                                        subscription list to your Bible you can also<lb/> put my
                                        name. I am now too far away from Jews to be able<lb/> work
                                        among them for this purpose. Since I resigned my<lb/>
                                        Rabbinate, I have very little to do with Jews. I
                                        quietly<lb/> look on at your quarrel with <persName>Dr.
                                                  Wise</persName>, may his name rot<lb/> moreover, I
                                        am convinced that nothing good can come of it. For<lb/> our
                                        sages have said that one must not dispute with Jewish<lb/>
                                        heretics and yet when we think we have more wisdom than
                                        the<lb/> sages of the Talmud, it can come to no good. That
                                        is why<lb/> I say about you what the wise man said to the
                                        Kusari,<lb/> "The intention is acceptable, but the deeds are
                                        not. However<lb/> you can do what you please while I remain
                                        a quiet<lb/> onlooker.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">Your devoted friend,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Abraham
                                        Rice</persName>.</p>
                    </body>
